Package: libzeep-dev
Section: libdevel
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, libzeep2.5 (= ${binary:Version})
Description: XML Library for SOAP servers written in C++ (development files)
 libzeep is an XML library that can be used to create a full
 SOAP server in c++. Code is generated by the compiler based
 on the signature of the methods that are exported as SOAP
 service. Makes heavy use of boost libraries.
 .
 This library also contains a full validating XML parser and
 an XPath implementation.
 .
 This specific package contains all files needed to develop new
 software using libzeep.

Package: libzeep2.5
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: XML Library for SOAP servers written in C++
 libzeep is an XML library that can be used to create a full
 SOAP server in c++. Code is generated by the compiler based
 on the signature of the methods that are exported as SOAP
 service. Makes heavy use of boost libraries.
 .
 This library also contains a full validating XML parser and
 an XPath implementation.
 .
 This package contains the shared library only.
